{"tw": {"2442400": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "情趣娃娃變成人", "steam_appid": 2442400, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442400/extras/ab722c411b1acb559e6195651e7f32d9.poster.avif?t=1773198140\" width=506 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442400/extras/ab722c411b1acb559e6195651e7f32d9.webm?t=1773198140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442400/extras/ab722c411b1acb559e6195651e7f32d9.mp4?t=1773198140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>聲優：綿雨たべ子 Wataame Tabeko 老師</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >李源在流星雨的夜晚許願，意外地讓自己的情趣娃娃夢夢有了生命，一開始，夢夢只會說話，不會動，身體也還是矽膠材質，在李源的細心照顧之下，夢夢的身體會動了，但要變成真正的人，還是需要兩人繼續努力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夢夢就像剛出生的寶寶一樣，對任何事都感到好奇，對李源也相當依賴，李源很享受這種依賴。夢夢畢竟是個情趣娃娃，在性需求上異常旺盛，每當她一本正經地說出色情的話語時，李源總是既害羞又興奮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有了生命後，夢夢身上無可避免地出現許多人類的習性，她會心疼李源上班辛苦，卻也會學電視裡的人罵髒話、沉迷網路等等，李源對她這些習性的處理方式，會決定兩人的結局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442400/extras/3faece86ea70a3a4796e7fd6ff715ba6.poster.avif?t=1773198140\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442400/extras/3faece86ea70a3a4796e7fd6ff715ba6.webm?t=1773198140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442400/extras/3faece86ea